'''''Kibera Kid''''' ni filime ngufi yashyizwe mu gace ka Kibera i [[Nairobi]],  [[Kenya]]<ref>https://www.cnn.com/2012/06/04/world/africa/kibera-slum-kenya-film-school/index.html</ref> . Yanditswe, iyobowe kandi ifatanya na Nathan Collett ku bufatanye n’abaturage ba Kibera<ref>https://nairobifashionhub.co.ke/kibera-kid-film/2/</ref>. Iyi filime y'iminota cumi n'ibiri yagaragayemo abakinnyi ba filimi muri Kibera mubikorwa by'ingenzi<ref>https://nairobifashionhub.co.ke/kibera-kid-film/</ref>. Yakinywe mu birori bya firime ku isi yose harimo iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Berlin kandi yatsindiye [[:en:Student_EMMY|Student EMMY]] ukomoka muri Hollywood<ref>https://www.interfilm.de/festival-chronik/en/filme?tx_interfilmfestival_filmlist%5BeventItem%5D=3325&cHash=79dad2cfb3164dac52a3216820d66057</ref> .  Byanditswe na BBC,  Reuters   hamwe na Al Jazeera Icyongereza<ref>https://kugomashorts.wordpress.com/2013/01/29/kibera-kid-a-short-tale-from-the-slums-of-nairobi/</ref> .  Muri Mata 2009, hafashwe amashusho yerekana amashusho ya Kibera Kid <ref>https://www.globalgiving.org/projects/kenya-slum-filmmaking/reports/?pageNo=7</ref>. Filime ndende yuzuye yibanda ku makimbirane ashingiye ku moko ndetse no kwiyunga. Iyi filime yagize ingaruka nini kuko yatumye hashyirwaho Hot Sun Foundation itoza urubyiruko rwo mucyaro gukora firime zabo<ref>https://stanfordmag.org/contents/planet-cardinal-2270</ref>. 

== Umugambi ==
Kibera Kid ninkuru ya Otieno, impfubyi yimyaka 12 yo muri Kibera abana nitsinda ryabajura bagomba guhitamo ubuzima bw'agatsiko no gucungurwa. Inkuru ni ibihimbano ibintu  byerekanwe ntabwo ari ukuri<ref>http://www.bongocinema.com/movies_african/view/kibera-kid</ref>. Ubugizi bwa nabi n'ubukene birasanzwe muri Kibera, nyamara hari benshi bazaharanira ubuzima bwiza nubwo ibintu bimeze nabi<ref>https://yamm.finance/wiki/Lola_Kenya_Children's_Screen.html</ref>.<ref>https://intro.africa/story/picha-marangi/</ref>

